Recently divorced Meg Altman (Foster) and her daughter Sarah (Stewart) 

have bought a new home in New York. On their tour around the mansion, 

they come across the panic room. A room so secure, that no one can get 

in. When three burglars break in, Meg makes a move to the panic room. 

But all her troubles don&amp;#039;t stop there. The criminals know where she is, 

and what they require the most in the house is in that very room.
